Package bacnet.scripts.core.vennDiagram

Class VennDiagram

java.lang.Object
bacnet.scripts.core.vennDiagram.VennDiagram
public class VennDiagram extends Object
Class for creating sets necessary in Venn diagrams
Providing a list of sets (through ArrayList) it will find intersections, unions and differences between all sets.
Author:
Christophe Becavin
